Mary T. Barnes, by Guardian, &c., Respondent, v. James R. Keene, Appellant. Decided July 2, 1886. Appeal from judgment entered on verdict, and from order denying motion for new trial. Shipman, B. L. & C., for appellant. S. H. Bandall, for respondent.

Before Sedgwick,.Ch. J., Truax and O’Gorman, JJ.

Opinion by O’Gorman, J. Judgment and order affirmed, with costs.
